<br />\n開放時間：1000-2000<br />\n👉🏻觀塘Hkgballboot 成業街18號新怡生工業大廈10樓F室<br />\n👉🏻太子基恩之家 荔枝角道95號7樓（太子站C2出口）<br />\n👉🏻旺角學聯 長旺道7-9號威特商業大廈9樓<br />\n👉🏻油麻地永旺行7樓 彌敦道557-559號<br />\n👉🏻銅鑼灣Think+holic 駱克道491-499號京都廣場21樓B號鋪<br />\n👉🏻灣仔富德樓4及14樓 軒尼詩道365-367號<br />\n<br />\n📌參與公投工會名單，公投前搵返所屬工會加入（名單陸續更新）<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/305DVqj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F305DVqj&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=e4362e75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/305DVqj</a><br />\n<br />\n📌義工招募：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/c57jXxVZCpVYzofn7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fc57jXxVZCpVYzofn7&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=385213a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/c57jXxVZCpVYzofn7</a><br />\n<br />\n#公投就是抗爭<br />\n#620罷工罷課公投<br />\n#向國安法說不<br />\n----<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會 | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=acb027f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JQLM2f&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=890084a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33hmGRR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33hmGRR&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=d68f5433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33hmGRR</a><br />\nTwitter: @hongkongstrike<br />\n網頁 <a href=\"https://hkonstrike.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkonstrike.com&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=dc6bfd98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkonstrike.com</a>"}}